{"tid":1767981,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[預言歌] 腎仔2011年首天馬行空講中晒而家","createTime":"2019-12-03T17:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T14:40:11.000Z","uid":125905,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9bc470d0f15a17e5548e827e45a3454d011fc744","tid":1767981,"uid":125905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T17:10:26.000Z","msg":"唔知wow左末<br />\n首歌2011年出 預言到中一中<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>紅字為重點</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n犁地灌水於後花園耕種<br />\n剛收割蕃茄煮餸<br />\n湯碗中 甜美 感動<br />\n憑著插畫繪寫人與事面容<br />\n可得到世間認同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">辛勞中 最想 靈魂感染大眾<br />\n不過看似純屬<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">發夢</span></strong><br />\n天馬要上半空卻負重<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">給指控 永遠給指控</span><br />\n可洗脫指控只得小眾<br />\n不過原來持續發夢<br />\n嘲笑偶爾可變動容<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一起衝 你我一起衝</span><br />\n衝不開也有精采的放縱</span><br />\n憑越野單車參賽歐洲飛縱<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">上路由爸媽歡送（熱切願我 成功）<br />\n胸膛中 無畏 感動<br />\n人類再不爭產能世界大同<br />\n階級間再不分輕重<br />\n壓迫 無蹤<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">炮火 再也不會服眾</span><br />\n不過看似純屬發夢<br />\n天馬要上半空卻負重<br />\n給指控 永遠給指控<br />\n可洗脫指控只得小眾<br />\n不過原來持續發夢<br />\n嘲笑偶爾可變動容<br />\n一起衝 你我一起衝<br />\n衝不開也有精采的放縱<br />\n或者當日也曾有火種<br />\n但擔心去路其實不通<br />\n然後大計跌入四維國度 失蹤<br />\n就此捲入既定軌跡中<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>天天照例運行在虛空<br />\n像循序漸進等夠鐘<br />\n是否甘心 永遠 被動</strong></span><br />\n不過愛上胡亂發夢<br />\n知道上到半空會極凍<br />\n給指控 永遠給指控<br />\n傷心與淌血必經之痛<br />\n不過原來持續發夢<br />\n嘲笑偶爾可變動容<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一起衝，你我一起衝<br />\n衝不開也有不枉的放縱</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/71IpK9bG2DI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F71IpK9bG2DI&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsfDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=8bb05574\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/71IpK9bG2DI</a>"},{"pid":"160f899414d680d0146a8d2c4424c110b546eddb","tid":1767981,"uid":125905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T17:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba19671c31128bdbc68b29dfa855ca61c3f4bb2","tid":1767981,"uid":125905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T17:56:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae80d14a8be87d559f5aed4c8cf44695e8c1bdf","tid":1767981,"uid":65573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T18:05:06.000Z","msg":"好前衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68041442dca9792c96f29127747c131e7014f2b4","tid":1767981,"uid":89999,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T18:08:17.000Z","msg":"咁樣計一人有一個夢想都中晒啦"},{"pid":"a06b283edcc27a04e4565733981f1f912ba0755c","tid":1767981,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T18:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f336bc2abc1a864bbe5e13d5fbf896ac608167","tid":1767981,"uid":125905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"68041442dca9792c96f29127747c131e7014f2b4","tid":1767981,"uid":89999,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T18:08:17.000Z","msg":"咁樣計一人有一個夢想都中晒啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T18:10:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">給指控 永遠給指控<br />\n傷心與淌血必經之痛<br />\n不過原來持續發夢<br />\n嘲笑偶爾可變動容<br />\n一起衝，你我一起衝<br />\n衝不開也有不枉的放縱</span></span>"},{"pid":"549801fa98ba62be8abd3468ef8315cf61bae440","tid":1767981,"uid":125905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T01:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 